{"tid":1220151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整左set常用《抗爭手語》請大家幫手傳播！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T09:17:46.000Z","uid":63171,"like":232,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"8486ec8048f13102ae2bf42adf12491d942a9686","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR8iaNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR8iaNC.png&h=2d679fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">戴住口罩好難大嗌！</span><br />\n就算你唔敢衝，唔係做物資站！<br />\n只要有個心，<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單一個動作就可以幫助前線！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要設備，搵個高處就可以做傳令官！</span>好似烽火台咁要幾遠傳幾遠！<br />\n<br />\n好喇！我諗唔到仲有咩講喇！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線咁辛苦頂住，就算唔敢行都請你幫手傳話傳物資！</span></span>香港靠大家去救！<br />\n跪求大家！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33389b190f35ac985d1139650c24a892a348192e","tid":1220151,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39beaeedcc00d77ba104fde5263f63f05ac22564","tid":1220151,"uid":14896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4813c5d9466ceb27ac449d47c0d81c10aaac8d14","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">頭盔</span></span>」：<br />\n兩手掌放在頭部上方，上下晃動，模仿頭盔保護頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbSyJ8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbSyJ8Q.png&h=298f6c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">索帶</span></span>」：<br />\n高舉雙手，以拇指及食指拉出一條水平的無形索帶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/px10o8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpx10o8Z.png&h=f4be4324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眼罩</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手成C形，放在眼睛兩邊，模仿眼罩保護眼睛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBp5AfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBp5AfO.png&h=b0372ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">口罩</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手成C形，放在嘴巴兩邊。類似眼罩動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmiBGVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmiBGVW.png&h=a458382c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長遮</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手上下握拳，在身前模仿雨傘撐開動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAsnCur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAsnCur.png&h=e434a081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Marker</span></span>」：<br />\n單手高舉，食指指天，模仿書寫動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zUqXrnZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUqXrnZ.png&h=dbb7401d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">哮喘藥</span></span>」：<br />\n拇指向下，放在嘴邊，模仿吸用哮喘藥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwehrn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffwehrn8.png&h=f16829bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">剪刀</span></span>」：<br />\n單手比剪刀手，橫向剪出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEnSfgC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEnSfgC.png&h=78d9ea73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">剪鉗</span></span>」：<br />\n高舉雙手，雙手分別展示剪刀手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72ZdJ96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72ZdJ96.png&h=fff4e61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保鮮紙</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手握拳打圈，「火車捐山窿」，模仿保鮮紙包裹雙手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYNZEJB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYNZEJB.png&h=2e66cd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">生理鹽水</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手模仿握罐，分別以順/逆時針轉動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0n3mW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0n3mW6.png&h=151ec515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">六角匙</span></span>」：<br />\n單手伸出拇指及尾指，六字手勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJk8x3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJk8x3V.png&h=6ebf8cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鐵馬</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手大動作劃出拱門形狀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOZJmXo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOZJmXo.png&h=f36b0f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">物資已足夠</span></span>」：<br />\n雙手在胸前打交义。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdQMjKb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdQMjKb.png&h=0a4db592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62a08dd433b055f117c4785508f0b5d9f1940e1a","tid":1220151,"uid":37757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbBvMpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbBvMpa.png&h=33bde432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫推 仲有依個，另一位手足熬夜整<br />\n希望大家當學下野"},{"pid":"8a34fd4fc3378a57285bf9197dddb15658f6d110","tid":1220151,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e000308ca956133cdaa93218fd4b7cd0867e361b","tid":1220151,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37de266338e5571dfb48b45869d08ddf06d5880","tid":1220151,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"好post要推"},{"pid":"70c487572bf0f952e07b1d4172dd7ba02042628f","tid":1220151,"uid":82521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"仲有叫first aid呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07418dc1dc0fae273e45ec4ab5f2da9f070f96a","tid":1220151,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f5a3f91ca8bcf6439d19f25e72899266f0ee57d","tid":1220151,"uid":49162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"冰袋"},{"pid":"4516cc18ea9a44a3a7f458b29ba77cb3f3b39d88","tid":1220151,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e45610d995465b3576c4e9e3213389e3cc0c0d","tid":1220151,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"686779a2ec1c8a7fa6880551ef0d8ba649dc52dd","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62a08dd433b055f117c4785508f0b5d9f1940e1a","tid":1220151,"uid":37757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbBvMpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbBvMpa.png&h=33bde432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫推 仲有依個，另一位手足熬夜整<br />\n希望大家當學下野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整好放上黎一齊用！鍵盤救港！"},{"pid":"08ca54ee9146baeee601d1a629bfa470ab6fa0fb","tid":1220151,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"除左物資類，有冇d關於行動？<br />\n準備衝/衝/停/退/有人受傷/靜，有人講話/對面出催淚彈"},{"pid":"e14aa43696ae20a0c8dbdeef92e5a66c6f02b82d","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c487572bf0f952e07b1d4172dd7ba02042628f","tid":1220151,"uid":82521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"仲有叫first aid呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"有漏請多提點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n需要時推出2.0，求大家幫推"},{"pid":"e98a703d027f508d74272318dd6ff3581fd371ea","tid":1220151,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6829f5ac3206f00ca63dd53fc72b76fa0ce71a4f","tid":1220151,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14aa43696ae20a0c8dbdeef92e5a66c6f02b82d","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c487572bf0f952e07b1d4172dd7ba02042628f","tid":1220151,"uid":82521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"仲有叫first aid呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"有漏請多提點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n需要時推出2.0，求大家幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"超人死光叫first aid"},{"pid":"5263a6d19a502e4de6d02b363809039613c7f930","tid":1220151,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"仲有個開遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9551997b83149866bc294c7b7303199d79dd353c","tid":1220151,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08ca54ee9146baeee601d1a629bfa470ab6fa0fb","tid":1220151,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"除左物資類，有冇d關於行動？<br />\n準備衝/衝/停/退/有人受傷/靜，有人講話/對面出催淚彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯 好可能需要<br />\n如果有巴打負責相關崗位，知道用開既動作，請向小弟提供<br />\n無限應激！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續幫推！多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><blockquote>引用</blockquote>"},{"pid":"07278436cdfbe6e820ebd1d2f7d2d1ea0c0766bc","tid":1220151,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見好多人現場真係做類似既動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"840b3b9d228f4bb24d0b8797e2d51dccd9551249","tid":1220151,"uid":133928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e60a519a60ff89bdf95dd051dac28be0f0ef1fa","tid":1220151,"uid":30527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e7a87a0280c13d3e3cfb6edad2e4e3742861d8","tid":1220151,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0fe8c4f4eebe29678cdbb9602cfd9c9d41015f6","tid":1220151,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"唔好整太多，頂盡十零廿個好啦<br />\n太多短時間唔會記得哂，亦好易混亂，揀最有用/重要既詞語，方便學習"},{"pid":"288fa08cf7b61f9b8df781fcdcc59606a41d94a9","tid":1220151,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"呢個唔錯"},{"pid":"317f3b8ce2afd444c8f0afb225bf3958be47aaf9","tid":1220151,"uid":89767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"樓主，除咗物件類之外，可唔可以都幫手推廣一下一個動作類嘅手勢？<br />\n<br />\n想同大家分享下喺突如其來嘅集體前進同後退，相信大家都可以容易理解到，單手手掌向前或者向後，但係其實仲有一個動作都好重要，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">停</span>啊！見過有人會拎兩隻手做T字，即係手語嘅停，但係喺電光火石之間，要拎兩隻手出嚟係浪費時間，同埋唔明顯（隻手伸唔夠高做個T頂）。其實可以揸實拳頭伸高，代表即刻停止行動，有hold住嘅意思，因為淨係需要單手，可以輕鬆配合前進同後退手勢，加強靈活度。<br />\n<br />\n另外發夢睇到有人集隊後退嘅時候，中間會有人唔知怕晒定怕雨喺度開遮，其實小小陽光小小雨點，企中間嘅人係唔需要驚同埋係無用㗎，夢境嘅世界中間嘅人把遮擋唔到雨，得前面嘅人先擋到雨，所以企中間唔該唔該唔好開遮，因為會阻擋到前面同後面嘅人進行手勢傳遞。"},{"pid":"6c98ca1ab8687dea1e046529024fba29846297b8","tid":1220151,"uid":222628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7aa45ff7da828a386195694e0f297c268bf4121f","tid":1220151,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"有無衝既手勢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca528f5f2b4189320a2126036790038d35eb0f5","tid":1220151,"uid":31961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e7e838b6e883ed5912831ec4641b0ba6bd17b8e","tid":1220151,"uid":202112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7ecb2de8f1df68b645615a22322802ab9afe18b","tid":1220151,"uid":174121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abdaa79552d4f8e9bd02c12b2e38b155e4e5c7dc","tid":1220151,"uid":251114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"317f3b8ce2afd444c8f0afb225bf3958be47aaf9","tid":1220151,"uid":89767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"樓主，除咗物件類之外，可唔可以都幫手推廣一下一個動作類嘅手勢？<br />\n<br />\n想同大家分享下喺突如其來嘅集體前進同後退，相信大家都可以容易理解到，單手手掌向前或者向後，但係其實仲有一個動作都好重要，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">停</span>啊！見過有人會拎兩隻手做T字，即係手語嘅停，但係喺電光火石之間，要拎兩隻手出嚟係浪費時間，同埋唔明顯（隻手伸唔夠高做個T頂）。其實可以揸實拳頭伸高，代表即刻停止行動，有hold住嘅意思，因為淨係需要單手，可以輕鬆配合前進同後退手勢，加強靈活度。<br />\n<br />\n另外發夢睇到有人集隊後退嘅時候，中間會有人唔知怕晒定怕雨喺度開遮，其實小小陽光小小雨點，企中間嘅人係唔需要驚同埋係無用㗎，夢境嘅世界中間嘅人把遮擋唔到雨，得前面嘅人先擋到雨，所以企中間唔該唔該唔好開遮，因為會阻擋到前面同後面嘅人進行手勢傳遞。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"非常非常同意要整套行動手勢<br />\n我琴